-No?
-No.

752
00:35:31.208 --> 00:35:33.333
You're just giving me the bed
because you feel bad for me.

753
00:35:33.416 --> 00:35:35.375
Get back on the bed.
I'm taking the floor.

754
00:35:35.458 --> 00:35:38.333
I don't need your pity. It's all yours.
See you in the morning.

755
00:35:38.416 --> 00:35:40.333
You just collapsed on it two seconds ago.
Take it.

756
00:35:40.416 --> 00:35:42.041
