That makes sense.

793
00:37:48.791 --> 00:37:50.833
Seems like you never really had a choice.

794
00:37:53.750 --> 00:37:55.041
Yeah. Right.

795
00:37:56.333 --> 00:37:57.458
Fuck that.

796
00:37:59.083 --> 00:38:00.000
Yeah.

797
00:38:00.916 --> 00:38:02.458
Yeah. Fuck that.

798
00:38:07.250 --> 00:38:09.500
